{"type":"user","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"type":"tool_result","content":"Exit code 1\n\n============================================================\nCoffee Shop Spring Boot Smoke Tests\nBase URL: http://localhost:8080\n============================================================\n\nWaiting for service at http://localhost:8080 ...\n  Service is UP (took 0.0s)\n\nTest: Health endpoint\n  PASS: /actuator/health returns UP\n\nTest: Static HTML\n  PASS: /index.html serves static content\n\nTest: Create drink order\n  FAIL: Expected 202, got 0: timed out\n\nTest: Create food order\n  FAIL: Expected 202, got 0: timed out\n\nTest: Get nonexistent order\n  PASS: GET /api/orders/99999 returns 404\n\nTest: Invalid order validation\n  PASS: POST /api/orders with invalid data returns 400\n\n============================================================\nResults: 4 passed, 2 failed\n\nFailures:\n  - Create drink order: Expected 202, got 0: timed out\n  - Create food order: Expected 202, got 0: timed out\n============================================================","is_error":true,"tool_use_id":"toolu_bdrk_01NU6LAC78MQq9RedhmXoCV5"}]},"parent_tool_use_id":null,"session_id":"69da0444-5130-4df0-8627-2b3179c5983f","uuid":"f482079d-c162-4fa0-9c82-66e2bfc2ab22"}
{"type":"assistant","message":{"model":"claude-opus-4-6","id":"msg_bdrk_01B9DbWotj2DShAuh92SoqV9","type":"message","role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"The POST requests are timing out. This is likely because the `OrdersPipeline` is trying to connect to Kafka when sending messages (the `KafkaTemplate.send()` call blocks or times out). Even though we disabled Kafka auto-config, the `KafkaTemplate` bean we created still tries to connect. I need to make the pipeline gracefully handle the case where Kafka is unavailable. Let me fix this:"}],"stop_reason":"tool_use","stop_sequence":null,"usage":{"input_tokens":1,"cache_creation_input_tokens":672,"cache_read_input_tokens":127135,"cache_creation":{"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens":672,"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens":0},"output_tokens":219},"context_management":null},"parent_tool_use_id":null,"session_id":"69da0444-5130-4df0-8627-2b3179c5983f","uuid":"73878cab-c43c-4204-812e-78fec20249be"}
