/application.properties: Spring Boot config (H2, Kafka conditional, Actuator)\n- orders-service/src/main/java/com/coffeeshop/orders/config/KafkaConfig.java: Conditional Kafka producer config\n- orders-service/src/main/resources/static/: Static web resources for Spring Boot\n- smoke.py: 8-test smoke test suite\n- CHANGELOG.md: Full migration log\n\nRemoved:\n- orders-service/src/main/resources/META-INF/persistence.xml: JPA persistence unit (Spring Data manages)\n```\n\n### Step-by-Step Log\n\n```\n[2026-03-14T06:40:00Z] [info] Analyzed project structure - 4 modules, Jakarta EE 10 + MicroProfile\n[2026-03-14T06:41:00Z] [info] Updated root pom.xml to Spring Boot parent 3.2.5\n[2026-03-14T06:41:30Z] [info] Updated common/pom.xml dependencies\n[2026-03-14T06:42:00Z] [info] Updated orders-service/pom.xml (WAR->JAR, Spring Boot starters)\n[2026-03-14T06:42:30Z] [info] Migrated 10 Java source files to Spring Boot\n[2026-03-14T06:44:45Z] [info] Created application.properties and KafkaConfig\n[2026-03-14T06:45:00Z] [info] Updated Dockerfile for Spring Boot fat JAR\n[2026-03-14T06:45:30Z] [info] Copied static resources to Spring Boot location\n[2026-03-14T06:46:00Z] [info] Docker build succeeded\n[2026-03-14T06:46:30Z] [info] Spring Boot started successfully (7.7s)\n[2026-03-14T06:46:45Z] [warning] POST tests timed out - Kafka connection blocking\n[2026-03-14T06:47:00Z] [info] Fixed Kafka graceful degradation\n[2026-03-14T06:47:30Z] [info] Rebuilt image successfully\n[2026-03-14T06:48:00Z] [info] All 8 smoke tests passed\n```\n\n### Error Handling\n\n- **1 Warning:** Kafka producer timeout during first test run - resolved by making Kafka optional with `@Autowired(required = false)` and `kafkaEnabled` flag\n- **0 Critical Issues:** Migration completed fully\n- **No Manual Intervention Required**"}],"stop_reason":"end_turn","stop_sequence":null,"usage":{"input_tokens":1,"cache_creation_input_tokens":454,"cache_read_input_tokens":90204,"cache_creation":{"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens